
Teleboy Live-TV Addon for XBMC
==============================

Steps to be done before using the teleboy addon:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* open &quot;http://www.teleboy.ch&quot; in your browser
* sign up (free) and login
* create your preferred channel list
* enter your login and password in the addon settings
* enjoy live television!

Credit:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A big thank you goes to "reduzent", the author of the watchteleboy
shell script, who did a good work in reverse engineering the
teleboy.ch specialities.
Most recent adaptions to teleboy homepage changes were contributed
by Francois Marbot - thank you!
